title: St. Martin's Organic Coffee House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Established 1979, this cafe is vegetarian except for fish. Vegan choices include day's soup, salad, the plain or chocolate flapjack. Has oat milk and dairy-free spread. Cakes are dairy-free but contain egg. Uses organic, whole food ingredients. In a rustic restored building with a garden area, upstairs, a piano, and open log fire on the go.
